      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HERE COMES RHEA (2) turned in a solid run fresh when finishing in the placings at this track in a Grade 6 (19.94). Goes very well here finding the frame in each of three starts. Can find winning form. CREEPER (4) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fourth (20.03) last time in a Grade 6 at this track. Cannot be taken lightly. CHEAT CODE (7) doesn't win out of turn but looks close to breaking through. Finished third (17.20) at this track last time making it two minors on end. Form here sound including three wins. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings three times from four attempts. Expected to be in this for a long way. CHAOTIC BOY (8) must be respected at his pet track and distance.",
